Package: shinycapture
Title: Browser-Side Capture Pipeline for Shiny
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R:
    person("Simon", "Niederberger", email = "s.niederberger@hotmail.com",
           role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: Browser-side capture pipeline for Shiny applications. Triggers
    capture directly in the user's browser — no server-side Chrome required.
    Captures Plotly charts at exact resolution via Plotly.toImage() and
    arbitrary HTML elements via html2canvas. The result is delivered as a
    base64 string to a Shiny input, ready for display or server-side
    processing (e.g. corporate framing, format conversion, download).
License: MIT + file LICENSE
URL: https://github.com/saemeon/shinycapture
